video.title: Fauda
video.synopsis: A top Israeli agent comes out of retirement to hunt for a Palestinian fighter he thought he'd killed, setting a chaotic chain of events into motion.

episodes.synopsis: Discovering that Abu Ahmad will attend his brother's wedding, Doron joins his old team for a covert strike, but the plan quickly goes off the rails.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Having tasted action again, Doron pleads with Moreno to rejoin the squad. Meanwhile, Amal determines to martyr herself to avenge her husband.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Abu Ahmad leans on Walid to organize an immediate retaliatory attack, and Doron and Nurit go undercover to close in on their quarry.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Doron sets his sights on recruiting Shirin to his cause, Abu Ahmad risks his life to see his wife, and Moreno sends the team on a daring daytime raid.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: A senior Israeli officer tries to smoke Abu Ahmad out of hiding. Ali fights suspicions of duplicity, and Boaz joins the squad on a risky ambush.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Blamed for the disastrous ambush, Doron takes matters into his own hands and asks the team to join him on a mission to set things right.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: While Moreno tries to track down the rogue team, Doron sinks his hooks deeper into Shirin and takes drastic measures to make a prisoner exchange.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: In the wake of the prisoner exchange, Doron disappears, Walid confronts Abu Ahmad about his tactics, and Moreno's boss threatens to dissolve the team.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: While suspicion grows between Abu Ahmad and his inner circle, Doron poses as a would-be suicide bomber to get perilously close to his target.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Doron gets a surprise visitor while waiting to learn his fate. Abu Ahmad lays out his master plan that could change the region's balance of power.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Doron's bosses give him the go-ahead to carry out his plan, but he discovers the toll his family has paid for his obsession with Abu Ahmad.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: While the team scrambles to give Doron backup on his mission into the lion's den, Walid makes a decision that could change everything.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Doron joins his old team for an operation to take out the mastermind behind a bombing attack -- and who also wants revenge against Doron himself.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Tensions rise on both sides as Doron's team intensifies its hunt and Abu Samara hands Al Makdasi an ultimatum. Shirin faces tough questions.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Rebuked by Walid, Al Makdasi doubles down on his renegade plan to exact revenge. Doron goes rogue during an operation to offer Shirin a way out.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Nidal's plan takes an unexpected lethal turn and backs him into a corner. Shirin reaches out to Doron, putting them both at risk.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Doron scrambles to protect his family when Nidal gets too close. Shirin puts a dangerous plan in motion. Walid learns some distressing news.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Sensing a chance to strike, Nidal regroups and leads a nighttime raid. While Walid faces interrogation, Doron takes Shirin under his wing.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Nidal defends his new allegiance to Samir. Captain Ayub blackmails Abu Samara into helping him lay a trap. Sagi's nerves jeopardize a mission.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: After discovering Nidal's true loyalties, Abu Maher joins in the effort to track him down. Captain Ayub and Naor escalate their plan to break Walid.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: With Doron grieving a loss, Shirin faces tough questions and the team carries out a rogue operation to get answers. Nidal sends Maher on a mission.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Worried that Doron is sinking into despair, the team rallies to galvanize him to action. Samir confronts Nidal. Abu Maher makes a discovery.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: An operation to bring down Nidal backs the team into a lethal corner. Abu Maher makes a heartrending decision, and Captain Ayub learns critical intel.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Doron faces a fresh threat as the scope of Nidal's unfolding plan becomes clear, while the team and Abu Samara move to intervene before time runs out.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Doron goes undercover in a risky, months-long operation, but his mission takes a sharp turn when surprise intel points to an imminent attack.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: The search for Fauzi intensifies in the wake of the attack. Doron goes back undercover but faces heightened suspicion and scrutiny.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Abu Mohammed gives Jihad a menacing ultimatum. A raid turns unexpectedly lethal. Doron pushes to extract Bashar to safety as the walls close in.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Jihad and Nasser act when an impulsive decision sends Bashar deeper into jeopardy. Avihai faces tough questions about the raid. Hila opens up to Doron.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: With Doron and his team close on their heels, an increasingly desperate Bashar and Jihad follow an audacious plan to elude capture.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: As the search for the hostages intensifies, Hila turns to an old asset, and Doron's squad prepares for one of its riskiest covert operations yet.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: A hostage takes matters into his own hands, making the team's stealth mission even more urgent. Bashar learns the distressing truth about his situation.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Saddled with a new responsibility, Jihad sees a chance to change his family's circumstances. Abu Mohammed faces fallout from the hostage debacle.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Hila pushes the envelope after the team's operation goes sideways, forcing Eli into a fraught decision. Doron faces a dire choice of his own.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Rejoined by an old ally, the team leans on Abu Mohammed while preparing for an all-out assault. Bashar discovers a deception and makes a desperate move.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Hardened, Bashar resolves to use Doron's own strategy against him. The team mourns a loss. Doron confronts Hila over her heat-of-the-moment decision.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Eli sends the team back into the field with a new member, while Bashar's plan for a knockout punch races toward a jolting end.
episodes.title: Episode 12
